White isn't alive in the corner, but killing it is surprisingly complicated. The vital point is A.

Black 1 looks shiny, but if Black 1, then White 2 - Black 3 - White 4. White 4 is sente and gives time for White to play 5. White lives.

If Black A, then White B - Black 4 - White 3 - Black 2 - White 1. Here, the throw-in at C is wrong for Black (White plays C, and Black doesn't have time to connect AND spend another move to make seki), so Black plays D. White plays C to make an eye. White cuts from the inside at E. MUST. And now, White reallys wants to play G, that's self-atari, so White plays F to capture 1 stone. This is sente since it unlocks a snapback, so Black must capture the 2 stones at the very top. With this, White can crawl out to the right side. White is not alive, but there is tons of aji, and Black isn't that much stronger.]LB[oa:4][pa:A][qa:B][qb:E][qd:1][ra:3][rd:5][sb:2][sc:G][sd:C][se:D][sf:F]MA[rc];W[mf]WL[30]OW[3];B[le]BL[30]OB[2];W[lf]WL[30]OW[3];B[je]BL[30]OB[1];W[sf]WL[30]OW[3];B[qd]BL[30]OB[1];W[rd]WL[30]OW[3];B[se]BL[30]OB[1];W[sd]WL[30]OW[3];B[sb]BL[30]OB[1];W[rg]WL[30]OW[3];B[qh]BL[30]OB[1];W[rh]WL[30]OW[3];B[ri]BL[30]OB[1]C[Clearly a blunder. A works and it's B+20.]LB[qi:A];W[qi]WL[30]OW[3];B[pi]BL[30]OB[1]C[A is a nice local tesuji. B also works. Both are better.]LB[qj:B][sg:A];W[qg]WL[30]OW[3];B[pf]BL[30]OB[1];W[ph]WL[30]OW[3];B[oh]BL[30]OB[1];W[qh]WL[30]OW[3];B[og]BL[30]OB[1];W[pj]WL[30]OW[3];B[kh]BL[30]OB[1]LB[oi:A]C[Just connect. Much better.];W[nb]WL[30]OW[3];B[pa]BL[30]OB[1];W[oi]WL[30]OW[3];B[mh]BL[30]OB[1];W[kf]WL[30]OW[3];B[ig]BL[30]OB[1]C[It looks wrong (thin?), but is good.];W[ke]WL[30]OW[3];B[kd]BL[30]OB[1]LB[kb:A]C[In this shape, A is a tesuji. The 2 stones are only 1 eye.];W[ld]WL[30]OW[3];B[md]BL[30]OB[1]LB[kb:A]C[A is better. Saving the 2 stones is wrong.];W[mc]WL[30]OW[3];B[ld]BL[30]OB[1];W[lb]WL[30]OW[3];B[jc]BL[30]OB[1];W[jb]WL[30]OW[3]C[White missed the monkey jump connect, so Black is rewarded for blundering. Tsk tsk.];B[ib]BL[30]OB[1];W[ia]WL[30]OW[3];B[kb]BL[30]OB[1];W[ka]WL[30]OW[3];B[ja]BL[30]OB[1];W[na]WL[30]OW[3];B[oa]BL[30]OB[1];W[jb]WL[30]OW[3];B[sc]BL[30]OB[1]LB[qk:A]C[A is the best ko threat.];W[kc]WL[30]OW[3];B[qb]BL[30]OB[1];W[jd]WL[30]OW